      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING CASCADE (6) was out of the placings last time but shapes well for this on his outstanding win a few runs back, getting around Bulli over 472m in 26.17. Expected to push the clock again here. MR. NICKO (1) is rarely out of the finish, recording 10 places from 20 starts. Finished in the minors latest when third (30.19) at Richmond and may be close to breaking through. Solid record here winning three races. The form out of his last race has been franked. Will give a great sight again. HARD SNIFF STYLE (3) turned in a moderate effort last time when sixth at Richmond over 520m behind Spring Witness (30.62) in a Grade 5. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. SWIFT WIND (2) placed last time at this track and distance - worth some thought.",
